AS part of helping investors and traders start early to reposition for robust returns, stay ahead of inflation and make the best of the pre-election in their journey to financial independence, Investdata Consulting Limited, on Sunday, January 2, 2022, held its regular Q1 Master Class. The event tagged ‘Actionable Trading Plans for 2022’, according to a statement by Ambrose Omordion, Chief Research Officer, Investdata Consulting, equipped participants with “best trading strategies for the first earnings reporting season of the new year.” Participants were taught how professional traders manage risks, and four simple steps for consistently profitable trading and investing, in addition to being helped to identify and forecast trends with precision and conviction. This is in addition to helping to discover the power of earnings and volume in any market cycle, planning as a successful tool for traders and investors, and five hot stocks for capital appreciation and five double-digit dividend-paying companies. Critical posers for self as investors begin their action plans, Omordion continued, include: where you want to be financially by the end Q1 2022 end, starting with positioning in the right stocks at the first trading day and week in 2022; how much money you hope to make from trading the peak of earnings season; are your current trading strategies and plans working for you, or do you need to research new strategies or new investment windows to trade? Also, he urged those who are disillusioned after losing money, or have a small profit size, to get the trade map being offered at the masterclass.